IMAPAccount work
Host localhost
Port 1143
User %USERNAME%
PassCmd "pass `cat ~/.mutt_work`"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType None

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
Path ~/mail/work/
Inbox ~/mail/work/Inbox

Channel work-main
Master :work-remote:
Slave :work-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "*"
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

Channel work-nn
Master :work-remote:NN
Slave :work-local:NN
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

Channel work-devops
Master :work-remote:DevOps
Slave :work-local:devops
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

Channel work-low
Master :work-remote:LowPriority
Slave :work-local:LowPriority
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *


Channel work-trash
Master :work-remote:"Deleted Items"
Slave :work-local:Trash
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

Channel work-sent
Master :work-remote:"Sent Items"
Slave :work-local:sent
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

Group work
Channel work-main
Channel work-nn
Channel work-devops
Channel work-low
Channel work-trash
Channel work-sent
